    public interface SingleColumnAggregatorRecipe
extends AlphaRecipe, RederivableNodeRecipe
    A representation of the model object 'Single Column Aggregator Recipe'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Multiset Aggregation Operator
    • Aggregable Index
    • Group By Mask
